* Check current version of splunkforwarder installed 
	--> If necessary download latest version 

* Move splunkforwarder tarball file from bdc ---> lmdc --> host

* Stop splunkfowarder using cmd (./splunk stop) in /opt/splunkforwader/bin  

* Place tarball in /opt and extract it. It will overwrite over existing splunkforwarder directory 

* Start splunkfowarder using cmd (./splunk start) in /opt/splunkforwader/bin

* Add username and passwd 

* Check if forwarder is on using this cmd : ps ef | grep splunkd 

